## 📊 Governance & Integrity Metrics (4.4)

### Performance & Integrity Targets
- **API Response Time**: <100ms (p95)
- **Continuity Score**: ≥0.75 target (weekly non‑negative delta)
- **Drift FP Rate**: <3% (adaptive goal)
- **Readiness Index**: ≥0.70 stable before adaptive gating
- **Override Density**: <2% of deployments last 30 days
- **Build Time**: <5 minutes
- **Deployment Time**: <10 minutes

### Quality & Governance Metrics
- **Code Coverage**: >85% (lift low-freshness & orphan modules first)
- **Cyclomatic Complexity**: <10
- **Technical Debt Ratio**: <5%
- **Documentation Coverage**: 100% (evidence hash entries intact)
- **SDLC 4.4 Compliance**: >90% weighted
- **AI+Human Coordination**: >90%
- **Design-First Compliance**: >95%
- **KPI Compliance**: ≥85% enforced / ≥90% adaptive
- **Continuity Negative Drift Incidents**: 0 unapproved

## 🚀 Common Tasks

### Adding a New Feature (Governance Augmented)
```bash
# 1. Create feature branch
git checkout -b feature/new-feature

# 2. Write tests
# 3. Implement feature
# 4. Run tests
npm test

# 5. Compute continuity delta & drift shadow scan
python scripts/governance/continuity_scan.py --update
python scripts/governance/drift_scan.py --mode shadow

# 6. Check compliance & readiness index
python scripts/compliance/sdlc_scanner.py
python scripts/governance/readiness_index.py

# 7. Create PR (include continuity delta + readiness summary)
```

### Fixing a Bug
```bash
# 1. Create bugfix branch
git checkout -b bugfix/issue-123

# 2. Write failing test
# 3. Fix the bug
# 4. Verify test passes
# 5. Check no regression
# 6. Create PR
```

### Deployment Process (Adaptive Mode Aware)
```bash
# 1. Ensure all tests pass
npm test

# 2. Run governance integrity pre-flight
python scripts/governance/continuity_scan.py --validate
python scripts/governance/drift_scan.py --mode $GOVERNANCE_GATING_MODE
python scripts/compliance/sdlc_scanner.py
python scripts/governance/readiness_index.py

# 3. Build application
npm run build

# 4. Deploy to staging
./scripts/deploy.sh staging

# 5. Run smoke tests
npm run test:smoke

# 6. If gating=advisory/enforced ensure thresholds met
# 7. Deploy to production
./scripts/deploy.sh production
```

